('088a53e0-83a2-441c-a256-137fb98b784e', '20386635-3e37-4bbf-b103-ebe1f75869d2', 'page', 0, 'Privacy Policy', 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy-policy', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n<head>\r\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n  <title>Privacy Policy</title>\r\n  <style>\r\n    body {\r\n      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      line-height: 1.6;\r\n      margin: 0;\r\n      padding: 0;\r\n      background-color: #f9f9f9;\r\n      color: #333;\r\n    }\r\n    header {\r\n      background: #2c3e50;\r\n      color: white;\r\n      padding: 20px;\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n    }\r\n    main {\r\n      max-width: 900px;\r\n      margin: auto;\r\n      background: white;\r\n      padding: 30px;\r\n      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\r\n    }\r\n    h1, h2 {\r\n      color: #2c3e50;\r\n    }\r\n    h2 {\r\n      border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;\r\n      padding-bottom: 5px;\r\n      margin-top: 30px;\r\n    }\r\n    p, ul {\r\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n    footer {\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n      font-size: 0.9em;\r\n      padding: 20px;\r\n      color: #777;\r\n    }\r\n  </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<header>\r\n  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>\r\n  <p>Effective Date: [Enter Date] | Last Updated: [Enter Date]</p>\r\n</header>\r\n\r\n<main>\r\n\r\n  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>\r\n  <p>[Your Project or Company Name] (“we,” “our,” or “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our website, applications, or services (“Services”).</p>\r\n  <p>We are committed to transparency and protecting your data in accordance with applicable laws, including the Illinois Biometric Information Privacy Act (BIPA) and other U.S. privacy regulations.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>\r\n  <h3>a. Information You Provide Directly</h3>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>Name</li>\r\n    <li>Email address</li>\r\n    <li>Any messages or content you send us</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h3>b. Information Collected Automatically</h3>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>IP address</li>\r\n    <li>Browser type and version</li>\r\n    <li>Pages visited, time spent, and referring URLs</li>\r\n    <li>Device type and operating system</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h3>c. Open Source Contributions</h3>\r\n  <p>If you contribute to our open-source projects, we may store your username and contribution history as publicly visible under the terms of the relevant open-source license.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>Operate and improve our Services</li>\r\n    <li>Respond to inquiries or support requests</li>\r\n    <li>Maintain open-source project contributions</li>\r\n    <li>Prevent misuse or unauthorized access</li>\r\n    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell or rent personal information.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>\r\n  <p>We may use cookies or similar technologies for website analytics, session management, and feature improvements. You can disable cookies in your browser, but some functions may not work properly.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>\r\n  <p>We do not share personal data with third parties except when required by law, with service providers bound by confidentiality, or when necessary to protect our rights or safety.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>6. Data Storage & Security</h2>\r\n  <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or disclosure. Open-source contribution data may be stored publicly as part of repository history.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>7. Your Rights (U.S. & Illinois Residents)</h2>\r\n  <p>You may have the right to access, update, delete your personal information, request a copy of the data we hold, and opt out of cookies and tracking. To request, contact: <strong>[Your Contact Email]</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>8. Third-Party Services</h2>\r\n  <p>Our Services may link to third-party sites or tools (e.g., GitHub, analytics providers). We are not responsible for their privacy practices.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>9. Children\'s Privacy</h2>\r\n  <p>Our Services are not directed towards children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from them.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>\r\n  <p>We may update this Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here with an updated effective date.</p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>\r\n  <p>If you have questions, contact:</p>\r\n  <p><strong>[Your Name or Organization]</strong><br>\r\n     Email: [Your Contact Email]<br>\r\n     Address: [Your Address or P.O. Box, Chicago, IL]</p>\r\n\r\n</main>\r\n\r\n<footer>\r\n  &copy; [Year] [Your Organization]. All rights reserved.\r\n</footer>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', NULL, 'This comprehensive privacy policy outlines how the organization collects, uses, and protects user data while providing its services. The policy emphasizes transparency and compliance with privacy regulations, including BIPA. The organization collects both directly provided information (like names and email addresses) and automatically gathered data (such as IP addresses and browser details). They maintain strict data sharing limitations, implement security measures, and respect user privacy rights. Special attention is given to open-source contributions, which may be publicly visible. The policy also addresses cookie usage, third-party services, and children\'s privacy, while providing clear contact information for privacy-related inquiries.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-08-14 16:14:44', '2025-08-14 16:16:35', '2025-08-14 16:14:44', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 467, NULL, 17, 18, 1, 0),
